10. CONTENT DELIVERY / DAILY QUOTE SCREENS
================================================================================

DESIGN APPROACHES
-----------------
- Card-based UI is ideal for quote content
- Tapping quote shows different visual presentation styles
- Bright/warm colors reflect positivity
- Illustrations and characters make content engaging
- Animations and effects turn browsing into engaging experience
- Shareable format essential (social media ready)

RECOMMENDATION FOR UNJYNX:
  * Full-screen quote card with:
    - Glassmorphic card floating over ambient animated gradient background
    - Quote text in elegant serif font (for contrast with UI sans-serif)
    - Attribution below in gold accent text
    - Category indicator (Mahabharata, Stan Lee, Odysseus, etc.)
    - Swipe left/right to browse categories
    - Tap to cycle visual styles (dark glass, pure text, artistic)
    - Share button: generates beautiful image for social sharing
    - "Save" heart button with animation
    - Bookmark collection accessible from profile
  * Morning delivery: Quote appears as first thing in daily review
  * Notification: Delivered via chosen channels (WhatsApp, Telegram, etc.)
  * 60+ categories means fresh content for months
  * Subtle ambient animation: floating particles, gentle color shift

================================================================================
11. FOCUS / GHOST MODE INTERFACES
================================================================================

WHAT MAKES GREAT FOCUS MODES
------------------------------
- Zen Mode: Set specific time, phone enters restricted state
- Notification shade disabled, no home screen
- More customized than basic Do Not Disturb
- Focus Mode: Pauses selected apps only
- Minimal, focused screen with only work-relevant apps
- Greyscale filter option makes phone feel like e-Ink device
- Distraction-free workspace hides all UI elements

RECOMMENDATION FOR UNJYNX "GHOST MODE":
  * Activation: Long-press the ghost icon OR swipe down from timer
  * Visual transformation:
    - Screen dims slightly, gains subtle vignette
    - All navigation chrome fades away
    - Only current task + timer visible
    - Background shifts to deep space/aurora ambient visual
    - Glassmorphic overlay with just the essentials
  * Behavior:
    - Notifications silenced (except emergency contacts)
    - Other apps blocked (optional - user configures)
    - Ambient sound auto-plays (user chosen soundscape)
    - Timer auto-starts (if not already running)
    - Exit requires intentional gesture (swipe pattern or long-press)
  * Ghost Mode Stats:
    - Track total ghost mode hours
    - Achievement: "Phantom" for 100+ ghost mode hours
    - Streak integration: Ghost mode sessions count double XP
  * Visual Identity: Semi-transparent ghost icon that "floats" slightly
  * End of session: Gentle "return to world" animation with stats overlay

