DESIGN PRINCIPLES TO LIVE BY
------------------------------
1. "Would a user describe this as JOYFUL?" (Amie test)
2. "Does this animation INFORM or just decorate?" (2026 standard)
3. "Can this be done in under 2 seconds?" (Friction test)
4. "Does this feel like someone CARED about every pixel?" (Linear test)
5. "Is this calming or stressful?" (Things 3 test)
6. "Would I want to SHOW this to someone?" (Shareability test)
7. "Does this SOUND right?" (Superlist test)

COMPETITIVE POSITIONING
------------------------
Things 3 = calm elegance -> UNJYNX = premium excitement with calm when needed
Todoist = clean power -> UNJYNX = clean power + unique channels + gamification
Linear = obsessive craft -> UNJYNX = same craft standard, consumer market
Superlist = delightful details -> UNJYNX = even more delightful + functional depth
Sunsama = mindful planning -> UNJYNX = mindful + AI-powered + multi-channel
Forest = gamified focus -> UNJYNX = gamified everything (not just focus)
